ATTRIBUTION
This project's Bluetooth protocol implementation is derived from prior
reverse-engineering work:

  * Gadgetbridge — https://codeberg.org/Freeyourgadget/Gadgetbridge
    (AGPL-3.0): the v2 Ambient Sound Control command layout.
  * SonyHeadphonesClient — https://github.com/Plutoberth/SonyHeadphonesClient
    (GPL-3.0): the MDR message framing, checksum/escaping, and service UUID.

